msgstr "FFmpeg 說明主題"

msgid ""
"This is a multifunctional search tool useful for local help searches\n"
"on multiple FFmpeg topics and options. The search control, to\n"
"find occurences on text obtained from the chosen argument,\n"
"is very similar to what grep does on the Unix shell, but here\n"
"it's done in real time.\n"
"\n"
"If you don't find support for a certain codec or other feature,\n"
"it's likely that your version of FFmpeg is too old or not configured\n"
"with those features."
msgstr ""
"這是一個多功能的搜尋工具，可用於本機搜尋\n"
"多個 FFmpeg 主題與選項。搜尋控制項會在\n"
"所選引數取得的文字中尋找出現次數，\n"
"這與 Unix Shell 上的 grep 非常相似，但此處\n"
"是即時執行的。\n"
"\n"
"如果您找不到特定編解碼器或其他功能的支援，\n"
"可能是您的 FFmpeg 版本太舊，或未設定\n"
"這些功能。"

