msgid "Images need to be resized, please use Resize function."
msgstr "影像需要調整大小，請使用調整大小功能。"

msgid ""
"\n"
"1. Import one or more image files such as JPG, PNG and BMP formats (even in mixed mode),\n"
"then select one as your starting point.\n"
"\n"
"2. Use the Resize tool if your images have different width and height dimensions.\n"
"You only need to do this once for the selected file to automatically resize the other images.\n"
"Otherwise, it's optional.\n"
"\n"
"3. Set a time interval between images, or for a single image if you\n"
"«Enable a single still image» option.\n"
"\n"
"4. Run the conversion.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"The produced video will have the name of the selected file in the 'File List' panel, which\n"
"will be saved in a folder named 'Still_Images' with a progressive digit, in the path you specify."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"1. 匯入一個或多個影像檔案，例如 JPG、PNG 與 BMP 格式 (即使是混合模式)，\n"
"然後選取一個作為您的起點。\n"
"\n"
"2. 如果您的影像寬度與高度尺寸不同，請使用調整大小工具。\n"
"您只需要對選取的檔案執行一次，即可自動調整其他影像的大小。\n"
"否則，此步驟為選用。\n"
"\n"
"3. 設定影像之間的時間間隔，若您選取\n"
"«啟用單一靜態影像» 選項，則針對單一影像設定。\n"
"\n"
"4. 執行轉換。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"產生的視訊將會以 [檔案清單] 面板中選取的檔案命名，\n"
"並儲存在您指定路徑中名為 'Still_Images' 的資料夾內，並附上遞增數字。"

